citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:00 PM on
02-NOV-16.
Arrived at address and knocked on the door, called the coordinator and facility representative and left messages.
Waited at least half an hour and left a business card with the attempted time and date in the door.
